room_title: Escape room "Escape From Venus II: Collision Course" by Room Escape DC in Washington, D.C.
room_description:
You and your teammate are en route to Earth after your recent close call crashing on and escaping from Venus. As you make your way towards our home planet, you pick up an incoming transmission, where you find out that an asteroid is on course to collide with Earth in a populated area for deadly consequences.
Your small craft is the only one close enough to the asteroid to have a chance at destroying it before the collision, though many of your shipâ€™s functions were damaged on your previous mission. Will you be able to repair your ship and figure out how to destroy the asteroid before catastrophe?
